  <brief_title>Phase II Pre-operative Vitamin D Supplementation to Prevent Post-thyroidectomy Hypocalcemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Placebo-controlled, Randomized Study to Evaluate the Effect of Pre-operative Vitamin D Supplementation on Hypocalcemia Following Total or Near-total Thyroidectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
